[SPEAKER_09]: I made the motion, so you second.

831
01:13:05,846 --> 01:13:06,467
[SPEAKER_09]: All in favor?

832
01:13:06,507 --> 01:13:06,587
[SPEAKER_09]: Aye.

833
01:13:07,919 --> 01:13:08,960
[SPEAKER_01]: Okay, thank you very much.

