[SPEAKER_01]: Congratulations.

844
01:13:33,936 --> 01:13:34,976
[SPEAKER_09]: She's the best.

845
01:13:35,016 --> 01:13:35,796
[SPEAKER_09]: Yes, second.

846
01:13:35,957 --> 01:13:36,277
[SPEAKER_09]: Second.

847
01:13:36,297 --> 01:13:37,077
[SPEAKER_09]: Okay, thank you.

848
01:13:37,357 --> 01:13:37,777
[SPEAKER_09]: Thank you.

849
