1303
01:44:05,364 --> 01:44:08,464
[SPEAKER_01]: That's a little bit more wide open, so it's not as much of a problem.

1304
01:44:09,245 --> 01:44:15,106
[SPEAKER_01]: But for some reason, at some point in time, maybe when the trees were six or ten feet tall, they planted them

1305
