[SPEAKER_01]: Yep, yep.

1376
01:48:26,542 --> 01:48:31,789
[SPEAKER_01]: You know, we've had some significant, my first week here, we had a microburst.

1377
01:48:32,130 --> 01:48:41,282
[SPEAKER_01]: Not only took out our system over here, our heating system over here, but also knocked down a number of trees.

1378
01:48:42,316 --> 01:48:46,539
[SPEAKER_01]: And it was actually positive because it cleared it out to some extent.

1379
01:48:47,360 --> 01:48:50,803
[SPEAKER_01]: We haven't had that over at Willis because it's a more confined area.

1380
01:48:51,483 --> 01:48:55,466
[SPEAKER_02]: And how fast and how responsive was the tree company you were using?

1381
01:48:56,607 --> 01:48:59,390
