1384
01:49:03,573 --> 01:49:16,116
[SPEAKER_01]: Yeah, and, you know, they bid it, you know, they would have, I thought I might have had the bid list here, but they've been responsive to us in the past, I know that, or else we wouldn't be using them.

1385
01:49:16,476 --> 01:49:19,097
