[SPEAKER_01]: Yeah.

1388
01:49:20,377 --> 01:49:24,519
[SPEAKER_09]: The one at L'Esprit that you referred to, they were out there very quickly.

1389
01:49:24,539 --> 01:49:25,679
[SPEAKER_09]: Yeah.

1390
01:49:25,959 --> 01:49:26,379
[SPEAKER_01]: Same day.

1391
01:49:26,479 --> 01:49:26,719
[SPEAKER_01]: Yeah.

1392
